file.name: shared-oas.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.3
info:
  title: Shared OAS
  description: Shared OAS
  version: 1.0.0

paths: {}

components:
  schemas:
    RunId:
      type: string
    BucketName:
      type: string
    Solution:
      properties:
        name:
          type: string
        status:
          type: string
        solver:
          type: string
        databagName:
          type: string
        bucketName:
          $ref: "#/components/schemas/BucketName"
        inputFields:
          type: array
          items:
            type: string
        outputFields:
          type: array
          items:
            type: string
        runId:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/RunId'
        creationTime:
          type: string
        completionTime:
          type: string
        metrics:
          type: object
          properties:
            accuracy:
              type: number
    Column:
      properties:
        name:
          type: string
        type:
          type: string
        usage:
          type: string
        numEntries:
          type: integer
    Databag:
      properties:
        datasetType:
          type: string
        fileName:
          type: string
        databagName:
          type: string
        bucketName:
          $ref: "#/components/schemas/BucketName"
        numberRows:
          type: integer
        numberColumns:
          type: integer
        columns:
          type: array
          items:
            $ref: "#/components/schemas/Column"
        creationTime:
          type: string
    PipelineTemplate:
      properties:
        name:
          type: string
        type:
          type: string
        description:
          type: string
        pipelineStep:
          type: string
        fileUrl:
          type: string
